        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), because he has dealt faithfully and diligently, and prospered in his labours. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Thou deliveredst unto me.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " He rightly acknowledges that all he had came from his lord, and that it was his duty and his pleasure to increase the deposit for his master's benefit. The long delay had not made him careless and negligent; rather, he had used the time profitably, and thereby added greatly to his gains. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "I have gained beside them",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
