        "text": "Alia quinque superlucratus sum.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " The good servant says, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Behold",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", as if he pointed with joy to the augmented wealth of his master. He does not speak boastfully; he does not praise himself for his success; he had simply done his best with the means entrusted to him, and he can speak of the result with real pleasure (comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
