        "text": "1 Thessalonians 2:19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). So in a religious sense the obligation to improve talents is even more imperative. \"The manifestation of the Spirit is given to each one to profit withal\" (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
